{"tid":964092,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★除夕被炒 OL突失控利剪架頸","createTime":"2019-01-01T04:38:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-01T05:13:58.000Z","uid":19454,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"f02503d9d595ba4b482967557090699f82d021c9","tid":964092,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T04:38:46.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】除夕最後一天上班，被「炒魷」傷心OL，情緒失控利剪架頸圖自殘。現場尖東科學館道新文華中心一間公司，任職文員姓甘（四十九歲）女事主，早前被公司解僱，昨日為最後一天工作。昨晨十一時許，她在公司收拾個人物品時，懷疑心情灰爆，情緒極為低落，突然激動失控，在辦公室內隨手執起利剪架頸，作勢企圖自殘。<br />\n<br />\n男職員安撫報警<br />\n據悉，公司內姓楊（卅六歲）男職員見狀，慌忙報警求助，同時他嘗試安撫女事主情緒。警員接報到場時，事主情緒已平復，並將利剪放下，她沒有受傷，但仍由救護員送院檢查，警方仍正調查事件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%99%A4%E5%A4%95%E8%A2%AB%E7%82%92-ol%E7%AA%81%E5%A4%B1%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%A9%E5%89%AA%E6%9E%B6%E9%A0%B8-015734922.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E9%2599%25A4%25E5%25A4%2595%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E7%2582%2592-ol%25E7%25AA%2581%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E6%258E%25A7%25E5%2588%25A9%25E5%2589%25AA%25E6%259E%25B6%25E9%25A0%25B8-015734922.html&d=HoBoMebGnLthbdL9qGoKX9r9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=514247ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%99%A4%E5%A4%95%E8%A2%AB%E7%82%92-ol%E7%AA%81%E5%A4%B1%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%A9%E5%89%AA%E6%9E%B6%E9%A0%B8-015734922.html</a>"},{"pid":"84a9a98bd92be8cb07159043058d51d4f4fee4ba","tid":964092,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T04:38:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faa625edec73323a00ba8cf8cd14f63f69ff6dd6","tid":964092,"uid":21488,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T04:39:37.000Z","msg":"中年失業 仲要文員..."},{"pid":"3d2587bc4efa38a787e06946f5f71ca880a99d42","tid":964092,"uid":18999,"like":0,"dislike":0,